Package: GPlinksR
Type: Package
Title: Building Gene–Peak Network for ATAC–RNA Integration
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Xinran", "Wang", email = "xwang210@usc.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Kelly", "Street", email = "kelly.street@usc.edu", role = "ctb"))
Description:GPlinksR constructs gene–peak regulatory networks for ATAC–RNA 
    integration by combining enhancer-based, promoter-based, and proximity 
    (closest-gene) mappings. Enhancer–gene links are obtained from the 
    PEREGRINE enhancer–gene datasets provided by AnnnoQ, while promoter 
    and gene coordinates are retrieved from EnsDb.Hsapiens.v86.
